data.description: Welcome home to the highly sought after Fields of Saint Michael community.Custom built end-unit, spacious townhome on a corner lot w/private patio, mature shade trees & perennials.Convenient location to bike to the Crow River, parks, lakes, paths, dining, shopping, & schools.Large windows w/vaulted ceilings bring in exceptional light & an open concept allows many options for furnishing.Thoughtful upgrades throughout including; newer carpet, fresh paint, updated lighting, gas fireplace, newer stainless steel kitchen appliances, newer furnace & roof. This home shows a true pride in home ownership @ every turn. Walk into potential equity w/the unfinished basement (check out the inspiration pictures!). The loft on the upper lvl could easily be transformed into a 3rd bedroom on the UL while the lower level has a rough-in for a 3rd bath, egress in place & ready to add a 3rd/4th bedroom w/ample space for a nice sized family room. Welcome home to 11247 16th where adventures and memories await.
